OnboardingV1.greeting_details1: Vivint Assist makes it easier to take care of your smart home
OnboardingV1.greeting_details2: whether you're home, away, asleep, or on vacation.
OnboardingV1.greeting_details3: You'll start getting things like reminders to lock up when you leave
OnboardingV1.greeting_details4: and help with conserving energy when you're away or on vacation.
OnboardingV1.few_questions_started: There's just a few quick questions before getting started.
OnboardingV1.few_questions_before: There's just a few questions before getting started.
OnboardingV1.housekeeping_ask: First, let's get some housekeeping out of the way.
OnboardingV1.get_to_know_you: Now that that's taken care of, tell us a little more about your home.
OnboardingV1.notifications_ask1: Are you okay with the app sending notifications?
OnboardingV1.notifications_ask2: This is how you stay posted with what's going on at home.
OnboardingV1.notifications_no1: That makes it harder to let you know what's going on in your home.
OnboardingV1.notifications_no2: You can always change this in the notification settings of your device.
OnboardingV1.geo_ask1: The app needs permission to use your location.
OnboardingV1.geo_ask2: This makes it easier to automate your home based on who's coming and going.
OnboardingV1.geo_ask3: (Don't worry, your data is never shared)
OnboardingV1.geo_yes: Great! Just say "Allow" to the pop-up.
OnboardingV1.geo_no1: Not giving the app permission to use your location limits what you can get out of it.
OnboardingV1.geo_no2: You can always change this in the location settings of your device.
OnboardingV1.home_location_ask: Is this the right location for your home?
OnboardingV1.occupants_ask: How many people call this place "home"?
OnboardingV1.animal_ask: Any furry friends running around the house?
OnboardingV1.therm_sc_ask: All we have to do is confirm your thermostat preferences and you'll be good to go.
OnboardingV1.therm_sc_home_ask: Here's what you've set for Home.
OnboardingV1.therm_sc_away_ask: Here's what you've set for Away.
OnboardingV1.therm_sc_sleep_ask: Here's what you've set for Sleep.
OnboardingV1.therm_sc_vaca_ask: Here's what you've set for Vacation.
OnboardingV1.therm_adjust_tab: You can adjust these at any time in the thermostat tab.
OnboardingV1.therm_ask1: Great, all we have left is setting your thermostat preferences.
OnboardingV1.therm_ask2: I'll help you conserve energy by adjusting your thermostat when you're away, asleep or on vacation.
OnboardingV1.therm_ask3: Don't worry, I'll make sure it's always cozy when you're home.
OnboardingV1.therm_home_ask: Here's what most people like for Home.
OnboardingV1.therm_away_ask: Here's what most people like for Away.
OnboardingV1.therm_sleep_ask: Here's what most people like for Sleep.
OnboardingV1.therm_vaca_ask: Here's what most people like for Vacation.
OnboardingV1.loa_ask1: Great, all that's left is setting up your scenes.
OnboardingV1.loa_ask2: Scenes make it easy to adjust multiple devices at the same time.
OnboardingV1.loa_ask3: You can simply launch a scene yourself
OnboardingV1.loa_ask4: or set it so that they adjust automatically as you come and go.
OnboardingV1.loa_ask5: To be safe, your permission will always be needed before adjusting your alarm and garage door.
OnboardingV1.loa_ask6: To be safe, I'll always ask before adjusting your alarm or garage door
OnboardingV1.loa_settings: Tap the buttons below to set what you'd like to happen in each scene
OnboardingV1.loa_settings2: Don't worry about getting it perfect now, you can always make changes later.
OnboardingV1.final_words1: Here's what I'll usually show you when you open the app:
OnboardingV1.final_words2: And here's where you let me know what's going on.
OnboardingV1.final_words3: Here's a quick home summary you'll typically see.
OnboardingV1.final_words4: And here's where you can switch between Home, Away, Sleep, and Vacation:
OnboardingV1.final_words5: It takes a couple weeks to get to know your home before you start getting reminders based on whether someone is home.
OnboardingV1.resume_session: Welcome back. Let's pick up where we left off.
OnboardingV1.therm_sched_already: Looks like you've already set a schedule for your thermostat
OnboardingV1.therm_sched_keep: Want to stick with your schedule?
OnboardingV1.therm_sched_dont_keep: Or use Vivint Assist to adjust your thermostat as part of your scenes?
OnboardingV1.rout_control_devices: Routines make it easy to control all of your smart home devices at once.
OnboardingV1.rout_example: For example, when you leave for the day, just tap "I'm leaving" to adjust your locks, thermostat, and alarm all at the same time.
OnboardingV1.rout_trigger: You can trigger a routine here in the app
OnboardingV1.rout_auto: or you can have them run automatically as you come and go
OnboardingV1.rout_tap_buttons: Tap the buttons below to set what you'd like to happen with each routine.
OnboardingV1.rout_change_later: Don't worry about getting it perfect now, you can always make changes later.
OnboardingV1.rout_done_set_up: Perfect. There's just a couple quick questions before getting started.
